Examples of configuration
	db connection
	credentials
	feature flags
	business logic config parameters
	scenario testing
	spring boot config
	dev/test/stage/prod config
	
Ability to push config into a service/production

Configuration files can be
	properties
	YAML
	JSON
	NOT xml anymore
	
	
Goals
	Externalized
	Environment specific 
		(config differently in diff. environment)
	Consistent
	Version history
		track and review version history of prop files
	Real time 
		Make change should get propogated.

